  "texts": [
    "• Individualized learning: Addresses the unique needs of each learner (Ness & Middleton, 2012).",
    "• Adaptive learning: Utilizes technology to adjust learning experiences in realtime (Carceles-Poveda & Giannitsarou, 2007; Kerr, 2016).",
    "• Differentiated learning: Adjusts learning approaches to meet individual student needs (Morgan, 2014).",
    "• Competency-based learning: Learners progress by demonstrating competency, including knowledge application and skill development (Gervais, 2016).",
    "In this paper, we focus on the adaptive learning focus of PL, namely, the use of technology to tailor educational experiences to the individual needs, preferences, and progress of learners (Midgley, 2014; Oppermann & Rasher, 1997; Paramythis & Loidl-Reisinger, 2003)."
